title: God Has The Final Say | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: God Has The Final Say | Joel Osteen
description:
When it seems like you are at the mercy of your circumstances, know that God always has the final say. The battle belongs to Him.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
